{"title":"不绑卡，解锁Cloudflare Zero Trust","date":"2025-08-19T09:01:56.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2025年8月19日","L":"2025/08/19","MM-DD":"08-19"},"link":"2025/08/19/2025-08-19-cloudflare-zero-trust-warp","tags":["Web"],"updated":"2025-09-13T07:00:04.858Z","content":"<p>众所周知，Cloudflare WARP可以用来安全加密互联网连接，而WARP分为二这几种类型：</p>\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n  <li>\n    WARP 1G流量\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    WARP+ 需要特定渠道获得License，1923837100 GB，基本够用\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    Zero Trust 几乎无限流量\n  </li>\n</ul>\n<p>而获取Zero Trust正常来讲需要绑卡，但是，我们今天用特殊方法获取Zero Trust</p>\n<p>打开Cloudflare Zero Trust，不要理会绑卡提示，打开左边侧栏=&gt;Gateway=&gt;概述</p>\n<p>拉到下方提示，点击：<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"  src=\"https://www.fc.cloudns.ch/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/image.png\" /></figure></p>\n<p>按照提示操作，注意！在这个地方：<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"  src=\"https://www.fc.cloudns.ch/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/image-1.png\" /></figure></p>\n<p>不建议使用默认邮箱，容易注册失败！建议自己添加一个</p>\n<p><strong>题外话：启用MASQUE协议</strong></p>\n<p>连接完别退出！点这个跳过绑卡验证：</p>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\">\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"  src=\"https://www.fc.cloudns.ch/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/image-2.png\"  /></figure></p>\n","prev":{"title":"Linux与个人市场——成也开放，败也开放","link":"2025/09/11/HjmnFla6g-"},"next":{"title":"为什么FydeOS在国内注定小众？","link":"2025/08/14/2025-08-14-unpopular-fydeos"},"plink":"http://www.091209.xyz/2025/08/19/2025-08-19-cloudflare-zero-trust-warp/","reading_time":"212 字约 1 分钟"}